name: The Mystery v1, v3, v4, v5 (Eternity Render 5)
description:
This last image is a catalog of all the Mystery forms so far. While the liquid mirror of v1-dv1 is only available on hicetnunc the others have been traveling far. v3-dv2 will be shown at pal projects gallery in Paris, v4-dv1 is pink and proud on Foundation and the tower of v5-dv2 (stack) will be seen in an video installation at Steve Turner gallery in LA. This image is like my diary entry for this period in time. A summing up of this idea, these forms which started in the physical world and were the source for my own contemplation. There is one missing...

This is 5 in a series of 5 renders. PNG file, 2480 x 3508 pixels
